        	<div class="why-cho_inner">
        	<h2>Cloud Migration</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="images/magic-rabbit.jpg" height=300 width=330>
Companies large and small all over the world are using cloud computing as a way to save money, improve resiliency and even experience better security. Migrating to Amazon Web Services even allows small businesses to have access to more advanced technology. 
<br><br>

WonderOps can help small to medium sized business save money by migrating from the traditional physical server asset model to the more flexible cloud computing model. No longer does a company have to keep purchasing capital assets every few years. Managing your infrastructure is as easy as managing software. 
<br><br>

At WonderOps we start with an assessment of your existing infrastructure and their workloads. We then help you create a business case for the cloud and illustrate what savings are possible. Finally, we manage the implementation of the design helping you get to the desired state and the advantages of cloud computing.  
<br><br>

WonderOps also offers Managed Services for your cloud operations once your migration is complete. By engaging WonderOps for Managed Services, you can increase your expertise with cloud experts while reducing your overall cost for information technology support. 

<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
